Software Design

                                     * * *

#Design and UML
UML structure
• Class name
• fields (- for private field)
• methods (- for private method, + for public)

A hollow triangular arrow head means that the block is extending the other
block.

A line to a plus sign indicates that the class is enclosed in another class.

<hr>

